  <md:title>Bill Clinton and the New Economy</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list id="list-00001">
<item>Explain political partisanship, antigovernment movements, and economic developments during the Clinton administration</item>
<item>Discuss President Clinton’s foreign policy</item>
<item>Explain how George W. Bush won the election of 2000</item>
</list></md:abstract>
