<exercise id="fs-idp76766192">
<problem id="fs-idm166266944">
<para id="fs-idm228041584">What were some of the foreign policy successes of the Clinton administration?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp1291296">
<para id="fs-idp140250976">Clinton helped to arrange peace talks between Israel and the Palestinians, and between Israel and Jordan. During his administration, the United States participated in airstrikes that helped to end Serbian aggression in the region of Kosovo and the state of Bosnia and Herzegovina.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
